    summary="The software component includes Niord, AnaRed, TabPer, Cal_Arr_Fre and Calc_Covid19, together with educational and research tools connected to publications, virtual laboratories and academic work."
    actions={[{ label: 'Projects', href: 'en/projects/' }, { label: 'Publications', href: 'en/publications/', variant: 'secondary' }]}
  />

  <section class="section section-tight"><div class="container"><div class="card-grid software-grid">
    <article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Software/record</p><h2>Niord v.1.0</h2><p>Software linked to calculation, modelling and simulation of parameters associated with wave energy and ocean-energy contexts. It must be presented as software/record, not as a patent, until the official document is available.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Academic software</p><h2>AnaRed V1.0</h2><p>Academic software mentioned in the CV 2025. Its public description should be expanded only with verified technical evidence.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Academic software</p><h2>TabPer V1.0</h2><p>Academic software record associated with the professional evidence matrix and CV documentation.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Academic software</p><h2>Cal_Arr_Fre V1.0</h2><p>Computational tool associated with frequency-related calculation and academic work in energy/control contexts.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Academic software</p><h2>Calc_Covid19 V1.0</h2><p>Software related to COVID-19 modelling and computational support for scientific analysis.</p></article>
  </div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
